Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're out! We're out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make chase at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One other thing, Lt. Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While in pursuit of them,\NEric-sama also reappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and has just returned to ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at 'em come! Look at 'em come!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry is faster and more agile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.29,0:01:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what are we going to do\Nwhen we get to Warship Island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll be okay!\N--How will we be okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to find\Nthe dragons' nest first
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so Grandpa Ryu can get better, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.63,0:02:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like that's\Ngoing to be an option...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The small fries have leapt forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open to the left and right!\NCrane Wing Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?! They have us blocked off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump onto a ship, kick the guys off,\Nand cut the links!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the only choice, obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't sound too bad to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy, Completely Surrounded!\NCommodore Nelson's Secret Strategy"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marvelous! A truly marvelous view!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, now! Do not let\Nthe attacks falter even a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do not hit the raft!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Commodore!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For so many years I've sought\Nthe Millennial Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.08,0:04:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elixir of immortality,\Nthe Dragonite, is now as good as mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! The commodore's flagship\Nsays his plan has succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says his attack is still ongoing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our mission is over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they fall into\NNelson Royal's hands now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Lt. Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:05:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare one paddleboat\Nand three proficient seamen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A paddleboat?! What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because a mast would get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're going\Ninto the enclosed area?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.73,0:05:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! It's dangerous! Go back inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave Grandpa Ryu all by himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous! Get back here!\NIt's your fault if you fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.08,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.68,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang in there a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise I'll take you\Nto the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That moves me to tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.66,0:05:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll break through the front lines\Nand take you to the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We've been hit from behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sanji! We've been hit! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for! We're sunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! We ain't been hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.49,0:06:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell thought\Nof this plan anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That's it! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! A ball's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do any more than this!\NDo something on your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Balloon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You impudent bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you damage one of my warships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.38,0:07:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NHit them with the Super Giant Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.82,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!\NThere's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire the Super Giant Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pirate ship has\Nbeen trapped up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.35,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A direct hit from that and our\Nship'll be blown to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.18,0:08:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay!\NI'll just bounce it back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.52,0:08:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid!\NI'll turn the ship about;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.29,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you guys work the rear sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hurry!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An eye for an eye!\NI got a shot ready for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Fire!\N--Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.05,0:08:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy cannonball hit\Nour main cannon perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.09,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and lift me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Howdya like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what happens when\NUsopp-sama gets serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too shabby, for a fluke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so full of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.37,0:08:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! I can do that anytime!\N--Wow... He hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.04,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're cool, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep Apis safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who're you talking to?!\N--Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's act quickly and\Ncut some links to open a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.27,0:09:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy.\N--Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.07,0:09:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.81,0:09:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sorry, Zoro.\N--Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.60,0:09:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report! What are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:10:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three people from the pirate ship\Nhave boarded portside Ship #1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Steel chains, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Think you can cut 'em?\N--There's nothing I can't cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then they're all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about coming out of the woodwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I like it when things are lively!\N--Sure, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I leave the small fries to you.\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the Nelson Fleet,\Nwe won't let you break through here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.64,0:11:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That's it! That's it!\NYou're so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up!\NChop those things up good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse you! How dare you\Nlousy pirates try to break my links?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture them, at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll maroon\Nevery last one of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.29,0:11:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come! Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.19,0:12:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Slingshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyaaaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.75,0:12:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know they were like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one chain left!\NLet's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye-aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Someone stop them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.46,0:13:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Eric!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done! Now the\NMillennial Dragon is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scared me--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Sicko Sicko Fruit guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "Sicko." The Sickle-Sickle Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl! It's time to hand\Nover the Millennial Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'll never give you Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.87,0:13:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it over like a good little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:14:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can chop you into pieces with\Nwind slashes at any time, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay a hand on the kid and you'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! I, Usopp-sama,\Nwon't sit by quietly either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.46,0:14:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made that wind slash\Njust now miss on purpose...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.10,0:14:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in my way,\Nand this time I won't miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow your entire ship apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's him.\N--Huh? What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tie the raft to our boat!\N--It's him.\N--Huh? What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Tie the raft to our boat!\N--Looks like he's planning to take\NApis hostage and steal the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.18,0:14:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--Looks like he's planning to take\NApis hostage and steal the dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! If you lay a hand on him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.66,0:14:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll take out Apis and Nami\Nand the others with his technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll use my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?!\N--Listen better!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking the Millennial\NDragon now! Nothing personal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:15:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight dirty! Give Apis back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric! Well done! Now, bring it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. This isn't for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.71,0:15:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only reason I obeyed you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to use the Navy's\Ninformation-gathering capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.92,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you were any different.\NYou tried to use me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hired you for a great sum of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've worked off\Nthat chump change by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.04,0:15:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no obligation to obey\Na sea lion like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sea lion?\NYou're calling me a sea lion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to use the Dragonite\NI get from the Millennial Dragon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to make myself perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay! You'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot that backstabber!\NShoot him! Shoot him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.73,0:16:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're starting again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to\Nget blasted into pieces,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'd better start rowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Please don't\Nharass Grandpa Ryu any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take him to\Nthe dragons' nest right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!\NLet go! Let go, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.11,0:16:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, girl. You're a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm taking the Millennial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never let you have\NGrandpa Ryu! Never! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.15,0:16:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any more shouting\Nand I'll chop you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.89,0:17:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn kid, giving me trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.28,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you running for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!\NYou want some of this? It's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Grandpa Ryu!\NEat lots and get better soon, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cute!\NIt really suits you, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! My ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu let out a sound...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.27,0:19:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can move! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.25,0:19:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the...?!\N--You don't suppose he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You can do it,\NGrandpa Ryu! You can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.78,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're flying!\NYou're flying, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! If the Millennial Dragon\Nis just going to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I don't care if we kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I need is its Dragonite, anyway!\NFire! Fire! Fire like mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:20:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! Run! Run to where\Nthe cannons can't reach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! Shoot him down, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.36,0:20:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance to run, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!\NAttack it with this ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir!\N--It must be shot down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! It's coming this way!\NShoot it down, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!\NShoot it, quickly! Shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.68,0:22:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.10,0:22:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! What are you saying?!\NDon't talk about dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I know. I will save Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.58,0:22:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And take you to the dragons' nest!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So try hard to stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.16,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.64,0:24:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to going to\NLost Island?! Try hard to stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Damn those Navy guys!\N--This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.55,0:24:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy can't swim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! What is this?!\NThe whole sea is shaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.92,0:24:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.65,0:24:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-H-Hey, now! What's that?!\NIt's coming this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.29,0:24:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.46,0:24:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Through the Sky They Soar!\NThe 1,000-Year Legend Lives Again!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
